com.qbpsimulator.engine.model

Class Activity

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.qbpsimulator.engine.model.Activity

  • public class Activity
extends Object
    A class that represents an element in the process model. Elements in process instances refer to instances of this class.
    Author:
    Madis Abel
